HEADWORD: Elaphure
<hw>El"a*phure</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zo⟦oum⟧l.)</fld>
<def>A species of deer (<spn>Elaphurus Davidianus</spn>) found in china.
